Japan Post Bank Co Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















japan post bank co ltd
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Banking
Sub-Industry: Banks
Japan Post Bank Co. Ltd. provides general banking services. The Company offers deposits, savings, loans, currency exchange transactions, investment trusts, national bonds, and other related banking services to individuals and businesses. Japan Post Bank also provides other financial services such as insurance agency and financing service.




